{"tid":1859112,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"澳門加強防疫　乘客搭巴士輕軌必須戴口罩","createTime":"2020-02-03T05:42:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T07:12:48.000Z","uid":76133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b3712c143c8dc57ffbdd3e2f1df6bcb3584b3c84","tid":1859112,"uid":76133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T05:42:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200203/bkn-20200203113637217-0203_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200203%2Fbkn-20200203113637217-0203_00822_001.html&d=sSzAGq%2B8hAhXqg0aovu9KRTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=1bc443b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200203/bkn-20200203113637217-0203_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎肆虐，澳門交通事務局表示，由今日(3日)中午12時起，所有巴士乘客必須佩戴口罩，否則車長有權拒絕乘客上車。<br />\n輕軌公司亦宣布今午1時起，所有乘搭輕軌的乘客均須戴口罩，站員有權拒絕未佩戴口罩的乘客使用輕軌服務。輕軌公司又稱，將繼續加強車廂及站點消毒，留意工作人員的身體情況，做好防疫工作。<br />\n交通事務局同時呼籲，乘客乘搭其他交通工具也應主動佩戴口罩，注意個人衞生，當局已要求各公共交通及相關管理公司加強清潔和消毒車廂及站點，留意車長及員工的身體情況，做好防疫工作。<br />\n<br />\n香港幾時跟?"},{"pid":"5bdf1c3011574d54a2396015901231a9f2faf2d6","tid":1859112,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T05:45:05.000Z","msg":"澳門 必須戴口罩<br />\n香港 不準戴口罩<br />\n<br />\n香港比澳門更緊貼國家 又然<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f6438a21397b18b75d54ea3b5cd9634bb8b67da","tid":1859112,"uid":151324,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T05:49:46.000Z","msg":"香港都無得買口罩 點跟"},{"pid":"a0dad98325c4002ee088e41b15ffc773f99bd530","tid":1859112,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T07:12:48.000Z","msg":"香港D廢老一定打司機<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}